Dialogue: 0,0:00:01.04,0:00:02.14,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,為什麼…
Dialogue: 0,0:00:12.99,0:00:16.32,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,為什麼…黃泉…姐姐
Dialogue: 0,0:00:17.26,0:00:18.33,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不要…
Dialogue: 0,0:00:19.79,0:00:20.73,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,叫我…
Dialogue: 0,0:00:21.16,0:00:21.81,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,姐姐！
Dialogue: 0,0:00:31.63,0:00:36.40,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,三年前的那天  我遇見了生命中重要的人
Dialogue: 0,0:00:38.82,0:00:41.29,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,父親  請注意腳下
Dialogue: 0,0:00:42.95,0:00:48.40,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,三年前的那天  我遇見了那個沉浸在悲傷中的女孩
Dialogue: 0,0:00:52.75,0:00:56.34,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那是一個大雨傾盆霧靄彌漫的午後
Dialogue: 0,0:01:06.14,0:01:11.56,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那是一次同樣背負著宿命的兩人的命運的相會
Dialogue: 0,0:01:14.00,0:01:16.74,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那是一切故事的開端
Dialogue: 0,0:01:13.49,0:01:17.96,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\a10\fad(1000,0)}\N\N\N\N\N\N「邂逅之際」
Dialogue: 0,0:01:35.58,0:01:36.37,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,土宮大人
Dialogue: 0,0:01:46.54,0:01:49.48,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,土宮大人  土宮大人…
Dialogue: 0,0:01:54.12,0:01:58.43,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這次的任務對我們退魔師一族來說
Dialogue: 0,0:01:58.51,0:02:02.79,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,甚至對於所有的聖者來說都是重大的損失
Dialogue: 0,0:02:07.17,0:02:09.60,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,雖然擊敗了怨靈
Dialogue: 0,0:02:09.90,0:02:13.84,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但土宮大人的夫人卻不幸遇害
Dialogue: 0,0:02:15.69,0:02:21.57,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,土宮大人當前正在進行將從夫人那繼承來的的喰靈白叡
Dialogue: 0,0:02:15.69,0:02:21.57,zhushi,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,（白叡：被稱為狗神的靈獸。白毛狗頭以及似龍的長脖、身體各處纏繞著鎖鏈。\N作為「吞食惡靈的惡靈這一被詛咒的最終兵器」封印在神樂家族祖先體內。）
Dialogue: 0,0:02:21.67,0:02:27.24,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,與自己的靈魂融為一體的封印儀式
Dialogue: 0,0:02:28.03,0:02:33.69,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,此前土宮大人一直作為盟主調和各個分家的事宜
Dialogue: 0,0:02:33.98,0:02:39.22,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但寄宿了喰靈後就要全身心地專注於除靈
Dialogue: 0,0:02:39.38,0:02:44.74,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,故而今後就由我諫山奈落擔此重任
Dialogue: 0,0:02:46.91,0:02:49.76,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,還請諸位助我一臂之力
Dialogue: 0,0:02:56.63,0:02:57.43,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你好
Dialogue: 0,0:02:59.28,0:03:01.00,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,能坐你旁邊嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:03:09.10,0:03:10.94,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,土宮神樂小姐？
Dialogue: 0,0:03:12.52,0:03:16.09,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,初次見面  我叫諫山黃泉
Dialogue: 0,0:03:17.35,0:03:23.86,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你父親作為土宮家第27代當家繼承了白叡
Dialogue: 0,0:03:24.74,0:03:29.92,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這是你母親從上代繼承下來的傳承了數百年的重大使命
Dialogue: 0,0:03:30.83,0:03:32.77,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,對於遲早將接過這權杖的你
Dialogue: 0,0:03:32.87,0:03:38.83,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,同樣身為分家一員的我會負責在暗中支持你的
Dialogue: 0,0:03:40.31,0:03:44.75,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,代替你那事務繁忙的父親  你的生活起居將由我家照顧
Dialogue: 0,0:03:46.19,0:03:48.56,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,請多關照了  神樂妹妹
Dialogue: 0,0:03:53.02,0:03:55.57,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,長大了不少啊  神樂
Dialogue: 0,0:03:56.52,0:03:59.50,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,還記得以前到這裡來玩嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:03:59.76,0:04:00.57,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不記得了
Dialogue: 0,0:04:00.91,0:04:04.08,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,沒事沒事  那時你還太小
Dialogue: 0,0:04:04.13,0:04:05.15,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不記得也是人之常情
Dialogue: 0,0:04:05.73,0:04:06.42,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是
Dialogue: 0,0:04:06.94,0:04:09.05,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,父親在分家會議之後不是還說過
Dialogue: 0,0:04:09.06,0:04:13.21,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,擔心自己能否勝任退魔師首領這樣的話呢
Dialogue: 0,0:04:14.44,0:04:16.19,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這使命如此光榮
Dialogue: 0,0:04:16.31,0:04:19.05,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這麼理不直氣不壯就麻煩了
Dialogue: 0,0:04:20.11,0:04:21.45,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不必有所拘束
Dialogue: 0,0:04:22.06,0:04:24.65,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我和你父親是老相識了
Dialogue: 0,0:04:24.93,0:04:28.17,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,把這當自己家一樣放鬆吧
Dialogue: 0,0:04:28.76,0:04:29.40,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是
Dialogue: 0,0:04:30.41,0:04:31.77,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,跟我來  神樂妹妹
Dialogue: 0,0:04:35.61,0:04:36.58,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你就住這吧
Dialogue: 0,0:04:37.86,0:04:39.86,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,從今天開始這就是你房間了
Dialogue: 0,0:04:42.80,0:04:44.88,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,明天去搬行李吧
Dialogue: 0,0:04:45.08,0:04:46.16,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,會派車過去的
Dialogue: 0,0:04:46.77,0:04:47.47,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不用了
Dialogue: 0,0:04:48.30,0:04:49.74,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不用跟我客氣哦
Dialogue: 0,0:04:49.87,0:04:51.72,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,要在這住上一段時間呢
Dialogue: 0,0:04:52.03,0:04:53.13,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,總有些必需品吧
Dialogue: 0,0:04:53.36,0:04:55.12,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,書啊  遊戲啊什麼的
Dialogue: 0,0:04:55.85,0:04:56.70,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,全部…
Dialogue: 0,0:05:10.99,0:05:13.18,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這就是…全部
Dialogue: 0,0:05:22.22,0:05:23.16,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,久等了
Dialogue: 0,0:05:25.15,0:05:27.41,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,房間雖然稍稍有些亂  不用太拘謹哦
Dialogue: 0,0:05:27.91,0:05:28.55,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是
Dialogue: 0,0:05:28.99,0:05:30.87,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,果汁好呢還是茶好呢
Dialogue: 0,0:05:32.16,0:05:32.94,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,隨便
Dialogue: 0,0:05:33.26,0:05:34.58,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那我泡茶了
Dialogue: 0,0:05:36.64,0:05:37.76,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,倒出些零食吃吧
Dialogue: 0,0:05:38.47,0:05:39.35,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,想吃什麼
Dialogue: 0,0:05:41.15,0:05:42.89,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,洋芋片吃的吧
Dialogue: 0,0:05:46.18,0:05:47.09,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,來玩遊戲吧
Dialogue: 0,0:05:47.47,0:05:48.42,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,有喜歡的嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:05:48.77,0:05:49.59,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,沒有
Dialogue: 0,0:05:50.84,0:05:52.39,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,平常都做什麼呢
Dialogue: 0,0:05:52.40,0:05:52.98,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,咦？
Dialogue: 0,0:05:53.41,0:05:54.53,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,一個人的時候
Dialogue: 0,0:05:55.06,0:05:56.16,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,修行…
Dialogue: 0,0:05:58.62,0:05:59.35,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那個
Dialogue: 0,0:05:59.73,0:06:00.50,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,什麼？
Dialogue: 0,0:06:01.10,0:06:04.69,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,能借用一下…道場嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:06:30.96,0:06:33.75,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真厲害  有得到土宮大人真傳吧
Dialogue: 0,0:06:34.10,0:06:35.17,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,素質不錯
Dialogue: 0,0:06:35.42,0:06:36.87,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,謝謝你
Dialogue: 0,0:06:37.34,0:06:38.66,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,要我陪你嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:06:39.83,0:06:41.11,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,就當作練習
Dialogue: 0,0:06:52.14,0:06:54.99,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,沒關係  全力攻過來吧
Dialogue: 0,0:07:12.22,0:07:14.82,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,以你這年紀來說刀法算很快了
Dialogue: 0,0:07:15.33,0:07:17.28,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,加以磨練會更強的哦
Dialogue: 0,0:07:18.26,0:07:19.19,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,一點都…
Dialogue: 0,0:07:21.03,0:07:23.09,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,一點都不強
Dialogue: 0,0:07:25.55,0:07:26.86,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,輸了就是輸了
Dialogue: 0,0:07:27.13,0:07:28.35,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,等等  神樂妹妹
Dialogue: 0,0:07:28.70,0:07:30.49,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,別想得這麼嚴重
Dialogue: 0,0:07:30.93,0:07:32.85,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,下次再努力就行了
Dialogue: 0,0:07:32.90,0:07:34.38,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,實戰中沒有下次
Dialogue: 0,0:07:35.29,0:07:36.33,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,實戰啊
Dialogue: 0,0:07:36.85,0:07:39.61,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,別看我這樣  還算很強的
Dialogue: 0,0:07:39.88,0:07:40.62,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,所以…
Dialogue: 0,0:07:40.63,0:07:45.06,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,父親說過實戰中不能選擇對手的強弱
Dialogue: 0,0:07:46.14,0:07:48.35,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,輸了就意味著死亡
Dialogue: 0,0:07:48.97,0:07:53.73,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,有使命的人死了就會導致上百個無辜的人死去
Dialogue: 0,0:07:53.96,0:07:59.01,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我們生為退魔師要對自己的生命負責
Dialogue: 0,0:08:00.27,0:08:02.02,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,父親再三叮囑過…
Dialogue: 0,0:08:03.29,0:08:07.30,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,就算是練習  輸了也要深刻反省
Dialogue: 0,0:08:08.16,0:08:09.25,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真古怪
Dialogue: 0,0:08:10.21,0:08:13.28,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,神樂妹妹的父親非常古怪
Dialogue: 0,0:08:13.39,0:08:14.34,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,怪…？
Dialogue: 0,0:08:14.43,0:08:17.13,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,還不止  外加性情乖僻
Dialogue: 0,0:08:17.35,0:08:18.15,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,乖…？
Dialogue: 0,0:08:18.54,0:08:19.88,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不管是贏還是輸
Dialogue: 0,0:08:19.94,0:08:22.07,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,受到誇獎就該會心地笑
Dialogue: 0,0:08:27.15,0:08:29.06,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這次輪到你陪我了
Dialogue: 0,0:08:32.32,0:08:33.07,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,來  這個給你
Dialogue: 0,0:08:37.18,0:08:39.18,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,神樂妹妹討厭吃什麼
Dialogue: 0,0:08:40.43,0:08:42.19,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,說是不要挑食
Dialogue: 0,0:08:42.22,0:08:43.26,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,父親說的？
Dialogue: 0,0:08:44.38,0:08:46.00,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,快說  肯定有吧
Dialogue: 0,0:08:47.06,0:08:50.17,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那個…皮蛋
Dialogue: 0,0:08:50.33,0:08:54.46,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,很好  輸了的話今晚的配菜就是蔬菜炒皮蛋
Dialogue: 0,0:08:55.03,0:08:57.72,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,神樂妹妹贏了就給你做喜歡吃的
Dialogue: 0,0:08:58.27,0:08:59.48,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好  遊戲開始
Dialogue: 0,0:09:00.13,0:09:01.32,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,還沒準備好呢
Dialogue: 0,0:09:01.53,0:09:03.88,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,遊戲也是輸了就是輸了  不能等
Dialogue: 0,0:09:03.92,0:09:05.91,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那樣…太狡猾了  黃泉小姐
Dialogue: 0,0:09:07.74,0:09:08.76,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,黃泉姐姐
Dialogue: 0,0:09:09.22,0:09:09.82,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,咦？
Dialogue: 0,0:09:10.86,0:09:11.87,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不要用「小姐」
Dialogue: 0,0:09:13.84,0:09:14.48,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,嗯
Dialogue: 0,0:09:19.86,0:09:21.99,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,意料之外的好吃吧  皮蛋
Dialogue: 0,0:09:22.34,0:09:23.88,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,嗯…
Dialogue: 0,0:09:24.42,0:09:25.22,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真的嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:09:25.56,0:09:27.36,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那明天也做皮蛋吧
Dialogue: 0,0:09:27.40,0:09:28.10,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,哎！？
Dialogue: 0,0:09:29.08,0:09:29.89,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,開玩笑
Dialogue: 0,0:09:31.12,0:09:33.99,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,對了神樂妹妹  來我房間吧
Dialogue: 0,0:09:35.19,0:09:37.02,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,在習慣之前一起睡吧
Dialogue: 0,0:09:37.60,0:09:38.32,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但是…
Dialogue: 0,0:09:38.80,0:09:39.58,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不願意？
Dialogue: 0,0:09:41.25,0:09:42.14,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那過來吧
Dialogue: 0,0:09:42.51,0:09:43.30,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,就這樣定了
Dialogue: 0,0:09:43.65,0:09:45.15,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,快去換睡衣吧
Dialogue: 0,0:09:45.54,0:09:46.71,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,繼續玩遊戲吧
Dialogue: 0,0:09:46.96,0:09:47.58,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,嗯
Dialogue: 0,0:09:50.17,0:09:52.42,zhushi,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\an8}（母親的病情並不樂觀。儘快趕到醫院。）
Dialogue: 0,0:09:53.80,0:09:56.37,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,黃泉姐姐的母親生病了嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:09:56.90,0:09:57.99,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這是集合口令而已
Dialogue: 0,0:09:58.28,0:10:00.89,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,因為就算是上課時之類的也不得不脫身
Dialogue: 0,0:10:01.11,0:10:02.26,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,集合口令？
Dialogue: 0,0:10:02.60,0:10:05.30,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,工作  雖然現在還是打工階段
Dialogue: 0,0:10:07.24,0:10:10.47,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,抱歉  我必須去
Dialogue: 0,0:10:27.17,0:10:29.76,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不  我沒事的
Dialogue: 0,0:10:32.30,0:10:35.88,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,抱歉了  可能會很晚  你先睡吧
Dialogue: 0,0:10:36.09,0:10:36.69,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,嗯
Dialogue: 0,0:10:53.23,0:10:53.97,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,黃泉
Dialogue: 0,0:10:56.23,0:10:57.60,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,處理班出動了
Dialogue: 0,0:10:58.01,0:11:00.89,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,預計到達現場時間為2100
Dialogue: 0,0:11:03.20,0:11:04.77,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是嗎  辛苦了
Dialogue: 0,0:11:05.50,0:11:10.49,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,還有這是上個月飛機失事死亡的海外派遣隊伍的活動記錄
Dialogue: 0,0:11:11.31,0:11:15.83,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,隊長三途河教授似乎在梵蒂岡搜尋著什麼
Dialogue: 0,0:11:16.52,0:11:20.17,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,三途河教授  是使用巫蠱術的家系呢
Dialogue: 0,0:11:16.52,0:11:20.17,zhushi,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fs28}（巫蠱為一種操縱毒蟲，並以咒詛害人的巫術，也叫蠱、蠱術。屬於黑巫術的一種。）
Dialogue: 0,0:11:21.33,0:11:24.63,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,他研究的主題是  殺生石
Dialogue: 0,0:11:21.33,0:11:24.63,zhushi,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fs28}（殺生石：千年前、被陰陽師收伏的封印著九尾之魂的妖力的結晶。\N一旦植入人體，雖然能得到無限的妖力，作為代價靈魂會被侵蝕導致肉體毀滅化為惡靈。）
Dialogue: 0,0:11:25.49,0:11:26.26,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,找到了嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:11:26.43,0:11:31.10,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不  雖然經過外務省詢問過相關負責人士
Dialogue: 0,0:11:31.42,0:11:33.17,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但還是沒有得到明確的回答
Dialogue: 0,0:11:33.67,0:11:36.89,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是嗎  繼續進行調查吧
Dialogue: 0,0:11:37.17,0:11:40.95,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是  再來是關於前幾天除靈作戰
Dialogue: 0,0:11:41.62,0:11:44.82,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,很遺憾還沒有完全確認已被淨化
Dialogue: 0,0:11:46.02,0:11:48.03,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,雖然怨靈消失蹤跡了
Dialogue: 0,0:11:48.18,0:11:49.92,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但還沒有確鑿證據
Dialogue: 0,0:11:52.06,0:11:54.91,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這是個即使有著喰靈白叡也陷入苦戰的對手
Dialogue: 0,0:11:55.53,0:11:57.24,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,留下禍根就麻煩了
Dialogue: 0,0:11:58.05,0:12:00.97,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,就算是微小的殘留思念也不要放過
Dialogue: 0,0:12:01.19,0:12:01.88,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是
Dialogue: 0,0:12:11.17,0:12:14.17,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,剛接任就這麼多辣手事件啊
Dialogue: 0,0:12:14.92,0:12:18.80,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,婆婆也真是挑了個棘手的時間交接啊
Dialogue: 0,0:12:30.78,0:12:32.28,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,抱歉  等很久了？
Dialogue: 0,0:12:34.01,0:12:34.73,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,回去吧
Dialogue: 0,0:12:35.92,0:12:37.50,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,學校怎麼樣  開心嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:12:37.94,0:12:38.59,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,嗯
Dialogue: 0,0:12:39.13,0:12:43.61,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,今天物理課上學支點  力點  作用點
Dialogue: 0,0:12:43.98,0:12:45.18,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,哦  好厲害啊
Dialogue: 0,0:12:45.55,0:12:49.92,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,學習至關重要  趁年輕要好好學習
Dialogue: 0,0:12:50.60,0:12:51.94,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,父親說的
Dialogue: 0,0:12:54.84,0:12:55.96,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我說  神樂妹妹
Dialogue: 0,0:12:56.25,0:12:57.21,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,喜歡吃什麼？
Dialogue: 0,0:12:57.34,0:12:57.96,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,咦？
Dialogue: 0,0:12:58.25,0:12:59.34,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,為昨天賠禮道歉
Dialogue: 0,0:12:59.63,0:13:02.45,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,今天做你喜歡吃的
Dialogue: 0,0:13:02.69,0:13:03.58,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真的嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:13:03.81,0:13:05.50,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,嗯  想吃什麼？
Dialogue: 0,0:13:07.58,0:13:08.88,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,什麼都可以哦
Dialogue: 0,0:13:12.86,0:13:14.10,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,奶油可樂餅
Dialogue: 0,0:13:14.61,0:13:15.86,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,奶油可樂餅…
Dialogue: 0,0:13:16.46,0:13:19.76,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,啊  那個很費事啊
Dialogue: 0,0:13:20.50,0:13:21.39,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不行嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:13:23.04,0:13:25.24,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好吧  做吧  奶油可樂餅
Dialogue: 0,0:13:25.49,0:13:27.31,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,神樂妹妹也能來幫忙嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:13:27.50,0:13:28.14,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,嗯
Dialogue: 0,0:13:28.42,0:13:29.90,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那去趟超市吧
Dialogue: 0,0:13:35.14,0:13:37.34,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,抱歉  神樂妹妹  叫我了
Dialogue: 0,0:13:39.29,0:13:40.72,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,一個人認識路嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:13:40.96,0:13:42.67,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,嗯  回來晚嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:13:42.93,0:13:45.14,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,應該…不會太遲
Dialogue: 0,0:13:46.16,0:13:48.12,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,對不起  我也說不準
Dialogue: 0,0:13:48.86,0:13:49.54,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,嗯
Dialogue: 0,0:13:50.32,0:13:51.23,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,對不起了
Dialogue: 0,0:13:53.06,0:13:54.72,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,媽媽也這麼說了
Dialogue: 0,0:13:56.47,0:13:59.67,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,讓我等著  說是馬上就回來
Dialogue: 0,0:14:00.74,0:14:03.81,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,所以我  乖乖的等著
Dialogue: 0,0:14:04.78,0:14:06.53,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,想著她能快點回來
Dialogue: 0,0:14:07.21,0:14:11.56,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但是…媽媽卻
Dialogue: 0,0:14:14.03,0:14:16.65,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,抱歉  抱歉
Dialogue: 0,0:14:20.97,0:14:22.15,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不會拋下你的
Dialogue: 0,0:14:24.98,0:14:26.64,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我會保護神樂
Dialogue: 0,0:14:29.66,0:14:30.55,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,一起走吧
Dialogue: 0,0:14:31.37,0:14:33.09,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,讓你看看我的工作
Dialogue: 0,0:14:34.85,0:14:36.69,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,沒事的  不想看嗎？
Dialogue: 0,0:14:40.47,0:14:42.62,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,來吧  和我一起
Dialogue: 0,0:14:43.42,0:14:44.26,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,一起？
Dialogue: 0,0:14:44.54,0:14:45.25,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,嗯
Dialogue: 0,0:14:47.58,0:14:48.30,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,嗯
Dialogue: 0,0:14:54.47,0:14:55.20,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,上來
Dialogue: 0,0:14:56.98,0:14:58.12,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,太慢了
Dialogue: 0,0:14:58.58,0:15:00.25,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,別嚇著她啊  岩端先生
Dialogue: 0,0:15:00.44,0:15:01.50,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你這樣子很嚇人啊
Dialogue: 0,0:15:01.70,0:15:02.88,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這孩子是誰
Dialogue: 0,0:15:03.32,0:15:05.55,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,私自讓平民看到絕密任務…
Dialogue: 0,0:15:05.56,0:15:07.47,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,她是土宮神樂
Dialogue: 0,0:15:08.22,0:15:10.72,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,土宮…難道是那個土宮家的？
Dialogue: 0,0:15:14.73,0:15:16.80,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這是納布先生和納布先生
Dialogue: 0,0:15:17.27,0:15:19.08,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,納布初次見面
Dialogue: 0,0:15:19.32,0:15:21.91,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,納布也初次見面
Dialogue: 0,0:15:22.08,0:15:23.30,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,他們是孿生兄弟
Dialogue: 0,0:15:23.40,0:15:27.03,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,一個是哥哥納布  一個是弟弟納布
Dialogue: 0,0:15:27.28,0:15:29.14,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,取一樣的名字嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:15:29.20,0:15:31.22,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這似乎是出生地的風俗
Dialogue: 0,0:15:31.33,0:15:32.36,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,納布
Dialogue: 0,0:15:32.45,0:15:33.76,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那孩子是新人嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:15:34.60,0:15:35.70,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我是櫻庭一騎
Dialogue: 0,0:15:36.05,0:15:37.73,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,雖然看起來年紀小了點
Dialogue: 0,0:15:37.90,0:15:39.17,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但這行人手實在不夠
Dialogue: 0,0:15:39.37,0:15:40.29,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,歡迎你的加入
Dialogue: 0,0:15:40.84,0:15:41.77,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我是飯綱紀之
Dialogue: 0,0:15:42.97,0:15:46.02,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,就算人手足夠也照樣歡迎年輕女性加盟
Dialogue: 0,0:15:46.28,0:15:47.25,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這是什麼話
Dialogue: 0,0:15:48.00,0:15:50.12,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,要是有其它想法的話我可不饒你
Dialogue: 0,0:15:50.23,0:15:53.82,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,當然知道  我眼裡只有黃泉你哦
Dialogue: 0,0:15:57.00,0:15:58.84,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,在這種地方做什麼啊
Dialogue: 0,0:15:58.98,0:16:02.15,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這個  拿著吧
Dialogue: 0,0:16:02.90,0:16:05.96,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,空壓式·退魔居合刀舞蹴拾貳號
Dialogue: 0,0:16:02.90,0:16:05.96,zhushi,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,（出自名匠邁克爾小原之手的會選擇使用者的退魔刀，\N劍輔最初使用的武器。其威力會隨著使用者的靈力而變化）
Dialogue: 0,0:16:07.22,0:16:09.18,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,今天從師傅那送達的新作品
Dialogue: 0,0:16:09.82,0:16:11.19,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我說  岩端先生
Dialogue: 0,0:16:11.62,0:16:14.53,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是土宮家的孩子的話  用這個是綽綽有餘吧
Dialogue: 0,0:16:15.02,0:16:16.64,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不是這個問題
Dialogue: 0,0:16:16.83,0:16:22.17,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,抽刀時拉動扳機的話  依靠壓縮空氣力量能使出刀威力達到平時的3倍
Dialogue: 0,0:16:23.41,0:16:25.24,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我是不是不該帶她來啊
Dialogue: 0,0:16:26.67,0:16:28.13,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,對策室致處理班
Dialogue: 0,0:16:28.87,0:16:29.89,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這裡是處理班
Dialogue: 0,0:16:30.62,0:16:35.10,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,根據情報  當前超自然災害源出現在千代田區神田附近
Dialogue: 0,0:16:35.33,0:16:36.36,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,迅速應對
Dialogue: 0,0:16:36.59,0:16:37.39,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,瞭解
Dialogue: 0,0:16:47.53,0:16:48.35,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那是？
Dialogue: 0,0:16:48.65,0:16:50.55,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不愧是出身土宮家
Dialogue: 0,0:16:50.67,0:16:51.80,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,竟然能看到
Dialogue: 0,0:16:52.37,0:16:54.53,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,果然是昨天的殘餘
Dialogue: 0,0:16:54.98,0:16:58.12,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,趁它被封印在結界裡  趕快處理掉吧
Dialogue: 0,0:16:58.39,0:16:59.99,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真正蘇醒了可就麻煩了
Dialogue: 0,0:17:00.63,0:17:01.40,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,要上了
Dialogue: 0,0:17:02.14,0:17:03.15,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,黃泉姐姐
Dialogue: 0,0:17:05.28,0:17:06.87,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好好看著  神樂妹妹
Dialogue: 0,0:17:07.63,0:17:09.35,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這就是我們的工作
Dialogue: 0,0:17:11.65,0:17:17.61,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我們是環境省自然環境局超自然災害對策室的處理班
Dialogue: 0,0:17:18.60,0:17:20.82,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,處理掉在人世間作惡的惡靈
Dialogue: 0,0:17:21.28,0:17:25.23,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,以及對人類持有怨恨的怨靈是我們的使命
Dialogue: 0,0:17:32.41,0:17:33.28,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,亂紅蓮
Dialogue: 0,0:17:36.43,0:17:37.46,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那是鵺
Dialogue: 0,0:17:37.96,0:17:38.76,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,鵺？
Dialogue: 0,0:17:39.22,0:17:42.63,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,寄宿於黃泉的寶刀獅子王上的靈獸
Dialogue: 0,0:17:36.43,0:17:42.63,zhushi,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,（寄宿在寶刀獅子王裡的靈獸。酷似紅色獅子的巨大野獸、尾部是無數的蛇。\N仍然跟隨在惡靈化後的黃泉左右。名字叫亂紅蓮。）
Dialogue: 0,0:17:43.79,0:17:45.95,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,靈獸  鵺
Dialogue: 0,0:17:47.80,0:17:48.76,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你個蠢貨
Dialogue: 0,0:17:49.51,0:17:54.20,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,把代為照顧的大小姐帶到這麼危險的任務裡去  到底作何打算
Dialogue: 0,0:17:55.12,0:17:56.05,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,十分抱歉
Dialogue: 0,0:17:56.61,0:18:00.07,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,可是你強烈要求下我才同意接她過來的
Dialogue: 0,0:18:01.22,0:18:03.22,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,再這麼擅自妄為可不輕饒
Dialogue: 0,0:18:03.45,0:18:04.23,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,明白了沒
Dialogue: 0,0:18:04.67,0:18:05.39,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是
Dialogue: 0,0:18:09.24,0:18:10.84,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,惹他生氣了
Dialogue: 0,0:18:11.34,0:18:12.42,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,對不起
Dialogue: 0,0:18:12.69,0:18:13.99,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,沒事沒事
Dialogue: 0,0:18:14.22,0:18:15.70,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,家常便飯了
Dialogue: 0,0:18:17.12,0:18:18.40,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,黃泉姐姐
Dialogue: 0,0:18:19.35,0:18:20.17,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,嗯？
Dialogue: 0,0:18:21.26,0:18:22.70,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,關於剛才的事…
Dialogue: 0,0:18:23.77,0:18:26.06,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,姐姐的強烈要求下…
Dialogue: 0,0:18:28.01,0:18:28.90,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,為什麼
Dialogue: 0,0:18:30.52,0:18:32.52,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這個嘛…是為什麼呢
Dialogue: 0,0:18:32.87,0:18:34.70,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,或許是想要個妹妹
Dialogue: 0,0:18:34.89,0:18:35.83,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,妹妹？
Dialogue: 0,0:18:36.93,0:18:38.92,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,神樂妹妹不想有姐妹嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:18:39.67,0:18:43.75,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我不知道  但是對方是黃泉姐姐就行
Dialogue: 0,0:18:43.88,0:18:45.68,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那就成為姐妹吧
Dialogue: 0,0:18:45.83,0:18:46.68,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真的嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:18:47.01,0:18:50.00,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,很好  從今天開始神樂就是我手下了
Dialogue: 0,0:18:50.21,0:18:51.85,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,咦  不是妹妹嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:18:51.86,0:18:54.68,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,對姐姐來說妹妹就相當於手下
Dialogue: 0,0:18:54.69,0:18:55.70,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,咦…
Dialogue: 0,0:18:57.27,0:18:58.92,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這個給你  是護身符
Dialogue: 0,0:18:59.15,0:19:00.02,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,護身符？
Dialogue: 0,0:19:00.26,0:19:05.83,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,嗯  作為交換等神樂再長大點才能做那工作哦
Dialogue: 0,0:19:06.16,0:19:08.28,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不然父親又要大發雷霆了
Dialogue: 0,0:19:08.71,0:19:10.28,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,嗯  謝謝
Dialogue: 0,0:19:11.74,0:19:14.48,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但是  能被責駡真好啊
Dialogue: 0,0:19:15.21,0:19:16.18,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,為什麼
Dialogue: 0,0:19:16.67,0:19:20.78,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我和父親不怎麼交談
Dialogue: 0,0:19:22.68,0:19:27.79,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,修行的時候很嚴厲  但除此之外就不怎麼說話了
Dialogue: 0,0:19:28.32,0:19:33.54,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是嗎  但能和親生父親一起生活真好啊
Dialogue: 0,0:19:35.21,0:19:37.46,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我是孤兒
Dialogue: 0,0:19:37.76,0:19:38.53,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但是？
Dialogue: 0,0:19:39.44,0:19:45.62,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我的雙親在我小時候被怨靈取走了性命
Dialogue: 0,0:19:46.86,0:19:51.13,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,把殺死雙親的怨靈消滅的就是現在的父親
Dialogue: 0,0:19:51.89,0:19:54.20,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我是諫山家的養女
Dialogue: 0,0:19:57.10,0:20:01.97,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那是諫山家代代相傳的寶刀  獅子王
Dialogue: 0,0:20:02.67,0:20:06.61,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,父親卻把它傳給了沒有血緣關係的我
Dialogue: 0,0:20:07.14,0:20:10.66,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,把我當成真正的女兒撫養長大
Dialogue: 0,0:20:11.24,0:20:14.48,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,所以我也打算好好地報答他
Dialogue: 0,0:20:15.86,0:20:21.30,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我會繼承諫山的宿命——身為退魔師的使命
Dialogue: 0,0:20:21.67,0:20:23.62,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,宿命  使命
Dialogue: 0,0:20:24.27,0:20:28.14,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,沒錯  這就是我存在的全部意義
Dialogue: 0,0:20:29.62,0:21:31.25,zhushi,NTP,0000,0000,0000,Banner;6;0;0,（咒文大意：不動明王慈救咒  曩莫三曼多縛日羅赧  戰拏摩訶路灑拏  薩頗吒也  吽  怛羅迦  悍漫  嚩多他  欠  佉呬）
Dialogue: 0,0:20:29.63,0:20:32.31,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnArial\fe1}namah samanta vajrânâm canda
Dialogue: 0,0:20:32.91,0:20:34.22,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnArial\fe1}mahâ rosana sphataya
Dialogue: 0,0:20:34.25,0:20:35.93,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnArial\fe1}hûm traka hâm mâm
Dialogue: 0,0:20:36.26,0:20:38.98,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnArial\fe1}vâtatha kham khahi
Dialogue: 0,0:20:59.69,0:21:03.53,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,老師  醫院來消息說媽媽的病情…
Dialogue: 0,0:21:03.88,0:21:06.88,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,嗯  去吧  祝早日康復
Dialogue: 0,0:21:11.34,0:21:12.68,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,一直都十分抱歉
Dialogue: 0,0:21:22.12,0:21:23.74,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,上課叫你出來不好意思啊  神樂
Dialogue: 0,0:21:24.86,0:21:27.68,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,每次都對老師撒謊真過意不去
Dialogue: 0,0:21:27.69,0:21:28.65,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,打瞌睡了吧
Dialogue: 0,0:21:29.67,0:21:31.13,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,還留著口水的痕跡哦
Dialogue: 0,0:21:36.39,0:21:37.05,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真是的
Dialogue: 0,0:21:38.28,0:21:41.45,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我的神樂怪臉收藏又多了一張呢
Dialogue: 0,0:21:41.45,0:21:43.31,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那種收藏最好刪了
Dialogue: 0,0:21:43.56,0:21:44.53,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,來
Dialogue: 0,0:21:53.81,0:21:55.23,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,黃～泉
Dialogue: 0,0:22:02.62,0:22:03.51,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,要加速了哦
Dialogue: 0,0:22:23.33,0:22:28.93,OP日文,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(200,200)}聖なる瞳が　痛みを映したら
Dialogue: 0,0:22:29.05,0:22:31.18,OP日文,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(200,200)}振り向いてごらん
